        "brief_summary": {
            "textblock": "The purpose of the study is to develop a clinical test based on breath analysis that can be\n      used for disease diagnosis or prognosis."
        },
        "detailed_description": {
            "textblock": "The study will seek to collect and analyze breath samples from a broad range of patients to\n      develop reference ranges and to refine the testing methods. Protocols for breath sample\n      collection and algorithms for analysis will be developed. Samples will be collected from\n      normal volunteers, persons with documented liver disease, organ transplant or with known\n      COVID-19 test results."
        },
